364
00:19:24,196 --> 00:19:25,230
Oh.

365
00:19:27,199 --> 00:19:28,867
You're my family, too.

366
00:19:31,537 --> 00:19:33,338
Any other questions?

367
00:19:33,338 --> 00:19:34,873
