387
00:20:37,269 --> 00:20:38,237
Young Master...

388
00:20:38,237 --> 00:20:40,739
seems to be in love recently.

389
00:20:40,739 --> 00:20:41,940
It's just...

390
00:20:42,841 --> 00:20:43,909
What?

391
00:20:45,944 --> 00:20:48,180
It's just what?

392
00:20:52,851 --> 00:20:53,685
