407
00:21:54,279 --> 00:21:55,647
But...

408
00:21:58,517 --> 00:22:00,619
I'll be the only one in the rest of your life.

409
00:22:05,624 --> 00:22:06,391
Answer me.

410
00:22:46,398 --> 00:22:47,933
I wish I could take you with me.

411
00:22:48,901 --> 00:22:51,103
Let me know if you need anything,

412
00:22:51,103 --> 00:22:52,037
I'll send it to you.

413
00:22:52,037 --> 00:22:54,206
Yi is so thoughtful.

414
00:22:54,206 --> 00:22:55,874
You should learn to be.

415
