417
00:23:01,313 --> 00:23:03,215
All right, we're leaving.

418
00:23:03,215 --> 00:23:06,318
I'll give him back to you as soon as I can.

419
00:23:06,318 --> 00:23:07,719
Auntie.

420
00:23:07,719 --> 00:23:09,121
Remember to miss me, okay?

421
00:23:09,121 --> 00:23:09,988
Good boy.

422
00:23:09,988 --> 00:23:11,390
